13a37b8e5ab87d0713","tid":105643,"uid":41784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"牌都係近年先有，冇牌又新開會比較難，因為有牌之後開始執正晒啲野。<br />\n首先，地土用途要合資格<br />\n第二，環保署要審批巡查<br />\n第三，機電署check機器，出車房牌，出師傅牌<br />\n第四，客源<br />\n<br />\n陀地嗰啲你肯俾都冇乜人收，報警又簡單又cctv"},{"pid":"4e76077747913b123afaca14355ec10b94b87d47","tid":105643,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:34:18.000Z","msg":"要識人拎貨"},{"pid":"0a019ced56205de4a12d2da95e49e010bcd0e96a","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要識人拎貨</blockquote><br />\n點識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5a60d71df5e7c09b405bf514e9e7d6f9f82093","tid":105643,"uid":37101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要識人拎貨</blockquote><br />\n點識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d7629c599ead7273862683ebf0f6638ca80bfb","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"讀到邊度先可以註冊做技工"},{"pid":"15c807d52c0fc7430f716e360b47413172c4cbc2","tid":105643,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左過黎支持下"},{"pid":"bf6bc8f96b424ac0ddbcb9d4ca5600db03c03b13","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左過黎支持下</blockquote><br />\n巴打開咗？<br />\n巴打有冇落手整 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c810971be41941e3b30903af330086b3e2e8b28f","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左過黎支持下</blockquote><br />\n巴打開咗？<br />\n巴打有冇落手整 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就係想開間車房同屋企人合作<br />\n但係我唔知我要咩資格先可以做師傳<br />\n同埋我屋企人都想學整車得閒幫下手咁<br />\n佢地又要咩資格？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"823c540eec69050a8b902641d5bae6399de93019","tid":105643,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左過黎支持下</blockquote><br />\n巴打開咗？<br />\n巴打有冇落手整 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係話你開左我黎支持，我都想開不過唔識整車"},{"pid":"921ad76bc7c70cf94df5a9a301515052f126d3d2","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左過黎支持下</blockquote><br />\n巴打開咗？<br />\n巴打有冇落手整 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係話你開左我黎支持，我都想開不過唔識整車</blockquote><br />\n我以為你過來人開咗tim <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72b970c8e4eb311eb099bc981b47d42aa68b550","tid":105643,"uid":73720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>50 萬係咪已經乜都搞掂晒有餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n50個？你想有啲咩？"},{"pid":"87f3bccc3cb4673fd3cd8bb1ebbf84240f1d5266","tid":105643,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:58:17.000Z","msg":"樓主想開車房,但又好似乜都唔知咁.<br />\n定係其實知,但係想聽下更多意見?<br />\n不過開左,連登仔有冇折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921596075cdc13115ec66f37f83bf4162386b3bf","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主想開車房,但又好似乜都唔知咁.<br />\n定係其實知,但係想聽下更多意見?<br />\n不過開左,連登仔有冇折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我其實都係同屋企人想搞返個生意<br />\n一路以黎既夢想同埋屋企人全力支持我<br />\n甚至五十幾歲人都同我一齊去學整車支持我<br />\n但係我就係想做資料搜集<br />\n想知道需要啲咩先可以開到<br />\n<br />\n就算開都係過三兩年先開<br />\n如果開得成<br />\n到時連登仔打個九折又點話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外我想搵個地方俾人自助整車<br />\n你知啦其實好多人係識整車不過冇工具冇地方<br />\n有個地方大家可以落手落腳整車交流都好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c7785a7ba6cde7f2eeba051ea6f637c291cc84","tid":105643,"uid":41784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要識人拎貨</blockquote><br />\n點識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去多d零件鋪攞貨，要同老闆吹多d水，熟左實有折頭，甚至月結，到o個再上去r多d水吹，隨時買零件疊舊豬頭骨"},{"pid":"17a4427672133a6af5cc3bca0b4bf6256cc96947","tid":105643,"uid":41784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要識人拎貨</blockquote><br />\n點識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去多d零件鋪攞貨，要同老闆吹多d水，熟左實有折頭，甚至月結，到o個再上去r多d水吹，隨時買零件疊舊<del>豬頭</del>狗骨</blockquote>"},{"pid":"82014b4c7bd13d32e22f8e23d7ddf84c529bdc0d","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:56:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n點識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去多d零件鋪攞貨，要同老闆吹多d水，熟左實有折頭，甚至月結，到o個再上去r多d水吹，隨時買零件疊舊<del>豬頭</del>狗骨</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n唔該晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4668d0957166b74f9b590537d2f68760f0b19beb","tid":105643,"uid":36723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主想開車房,但又好似乜都唔知咁.<br />\n定係其實知,但係想聽下更多意見?<br />\n不過開左,連登仔有冇折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我其實都係同屋企人想搞返個生意<br />\n一路以黎既夢想同埋屋企人全力支持我<br />\n甚至五十幾歲人都同我一齊去學整車支持我<br />\n但係我就係想做資料搜集<br />\n想知道需要啲咩先可以開到<br />\n<br />\n就算開都係過三兩年先開<br />\n如果開得成<br />\n到時連登仔打個九折又點話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外我想<span style=\"color: red;\">搵個地方俾人自助整車<br />\n你知啦其實好多人係識整車不過冇工具冇地方<br />\n有個地方大家可以落手落腳整車交流都好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n此起都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b2bbed3bd43f1da4e08489849a5597e8080d77","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主想開車房,但又好似乜都唔知咁.<br />\n定係其實知,但係想聽下更多意見?<br />\n不過開左,連登仔有冇折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我其實都係同屋企人想搞返個生意<br />\n一路以黎既夢想同埋屋企人全力支持我<br />\n甚至五十幾歲人都同我一齊去學整車支持我<br />\n但係我就係想做資料搜集<br />\n想知道需要啲咩先可以開到<br />\n<br />\n就算開都係過三兩年先開<br />\n如果開得成<br />\n到時連登仔打個九折又點話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外我想<span style=\"color: red;\">搵個地方俾人自助整車<br />\n你知啦其實好多人係識整車不過冇工具冇地方<br />\n有個地方大家可以落手落腳整車交流都好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n此起都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣諗咗好耐<br />\n點解有自助洗車唔可以有自助整車<br />\n不過要實行就仲有好長既路要行"},{"pid":"0cc42890be57f0336f50b41713c8687eaa4e6c10","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc787a2c487deaea0a2770c84d9ec7939eb5b6c1","tid":105643,"uid":68842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T23:16:09.000Z","msg":"Support <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74186effdcf7cbddec024a17578137c0d345cad8","tid":105643,"uid":48460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T00:44:43.000Z","msg":"雖然唔識不過覺得自助整車idea幾好<br />\n祝你成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece1e8de68ea9207010b3d86f1a95dc532eeb9d3","tid":105643,"uid":68375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T00:51:22.000Z","msg":"自助整車，條友有咩損傷意外保險點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7782564be47cea31eb62f1fd4cdb2500ac1e6cc","tid":105643,"uid":32013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T00:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lidk09fh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flidk09fh&h=6c22ebc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手搵咗啲資料<br />\n呢一行入場費都幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5b7c99420d41db8c0d9537cacbd1a5adcfb2f9","tid":105643,"uid":32013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T01:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n呢樣諗咗好耐<br />\n點解有自助洗車唔可以有自助整車<br />\n不過要實行就仲有好長既路要行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打個諗法好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講出好多車迷心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但大部份香港人當汽車只係一件運輸工具，好少人會/識落手落腳整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPadax Bxx賣吓Facebook廣告都有咁多生意，相信巴打向呢方面發展一定得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135820387e88701ac4960c389e96e16be0c04ab3","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/lidk09fh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flidk09fh&h=6c22ebc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手搵咗啲資料<br />\n呢一行入場費都幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n整身有客源有設備又唔同既<br />\n汽車美容連塊抹車布都可能一千蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1338fe98c1550374e7aaa80faa141a4964365718","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n呢樣諗咗好耐<br />\n點解有自助洗車唔可以有自助整車<br />\n不過要實行就仲有好長既路要行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打個諗法好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講出好多車迷心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但大部份香港人當汽車只係一件運輸工具，好少人會/識落手落腳整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPadax Bxx賣吓Facebook廣告都有咁多生意，相信巴打向呢方面發展一定得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗住有個識整車既師傅喺度<br />\n一邊車房一邊自助車房<br />\n啲人又可以請教師傳唔怕唔識整<br />\n又可以 enjoy 整車樂趣"},{"pid":"933c99e3b0a6c04dc4bb50f305394faa6c9adb44","tid":105643,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主想開車房,但又好似乜都唔知咁.<br />\n定係其實知,但係想聽下更多意見?<br />\n不過開左,連登仔有冇折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係law, 開得一定做左好先會知.<br />\n以我所知要買電腦check車唔平, 尤其歐洲車."},{"pid":"dc26d263acb6544c85331016247a4821bb332e8d","tid":105643,"uid":28003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"幾年前已經有諗過自助整車 不過 因為安全問題 所以冇再諗落 萬一有人係個場度整整下車 有意外發生 咁係佢自己問題 定係你問題"},{"pid":"9ea8e97c3ce41a73f0f79d98c4f5f4e156bead8f","tid":105643,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾年前已經有諗過自助整車 不過 因為安全問題 所以冇再諗落 萬一有人係個場度整整下車 有意外發生 咁係佢自己問題 定係你問題</blockquote><br />\n所以一定有師傅睇住先<br />\n當外來人係學徒身份得唔得？"},{"pid":"5217c6dcad9a215684170bfcc7e599e8de3ac87c","tid":105643,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾年前已經有諗過自助整車 不過 因為安全問題 所以冇再諗落 萬一有人係個場度整整下車 有意外發生 咁係佢自己問題 定係你問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係個客問題, 個場合法做驗好無問題就得.<br />\n<br />\n但最大問題係, 整車工具係好貴的, 整欄左邊個賠, 點計先難搞."},{"pid":"3cb9db8a4c9ec285dbdc01ae5cef47b5a0d0bb3f","tid":105643,"uid":63919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"搵人帶入行 <br />\n做整車定咩？<br />\n行頭窄 新手入行好難做<br />\n<br />\n屋企仲車行+車房"},{"pid":"93db9c097043c59b8fec0318117a2980989ab5ac","tid":105643,"uid":28003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾年前已經有諗過自助整車 不過 因為安全問題 所以冇再諗落 萬一有人係個場度整整下車 有意外發生 咁係佢自己問題 定係你問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係個客問題, 個場合法做驗好無問題就得.<br />\n<br />\n但最大問題係, 整車工具係好貴的, 整欄左邊個賠, 點計先難搞.</blockquote><br />\n咪係囉 你話香港人全部都自律就話遮"},{"pid":"c05fb7da04b0d770fb1f445416a7fd49fa1d2903","tid":105643,"uid":28003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾年前已經有諗過自助整車 不過 因為安全問題 所以冇再諗落 萬一有人係個場度整整下車 有意外發生 咁係佢自己問題 定係你問題</blockquote><br />\n所以一定有師傅睇住先<br />\n當外來人係學徒身份得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n你租地唔洗錢？ 每年保養工具唔洗錢？ 你請個師傅返黎唔洗錢？ 每人收幾多錢先回到本？"},{"pid":"55f879cfcfd4a71607b41092f5e0837f4d328dcd","tid":105643,"uid":51272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"樓主開左講聲<br />\n細細個已經好鐘意車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直好想做整車仔但好低人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}